movie_name: Creature from Big Muddy: An Illinois Bigfoot Legend
short_description: In the early 1970's in Murphysboro, Illinois, the town was terrorized by a creature that was thought to come out of a local river called the Big Muddy. This documentary explores the legend of The Big Muddy Monster.
